{"tid":2423676,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 千與千尋都拍真人版","createTime":"2021-02-26T05:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:36:16.000Z","uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dac829bf42a2ba5ba70ed4e9564ad581ddeced48","tid":2423676,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/spirited-away-stage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fentertainment%2Fspirited-away-stage%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd61Df25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=ced245e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/spirited-away-stage/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1396c67be09c1a89bff851674608543b4cebde98","tid":2423676,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"《千與千尋》官方確認真人化！橋本環奈與上白石萌音主演舞台劇<br />\nBy LikeJapan 編輯部 / 2021-02-26<br />\n<br />\n吉卜力的超名作《千與千尋》剛剛確認了真人化的消息，作為東寶成立90周年的紀念作品，它終於要被首次舞台劇化了。而這部刻已確認找來了超人氣女星，橋本環奈與上白石萌音主演，她們分別也會演主角千尋。<br />\n<br />\n這一部2001年在日本推出的作品，由大師宮崎駿負責劇本、導演，並在日本國內得到316億8000萬日圓的收入。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：(2020年12月)《千與千尋》票房突然再發力 拉開與「無限列車」的距離!?<br />\n<br />\n舞台導演John Caird對擔任主演的橋本與上白石寄予厚望。首次出演舞台劇的橋本因為其美聲和神情與千尋很相似而被提拔為主角。橋本干勁十足地表示「我希望可以以自己的方式自在地享受今次的演出」以及「為了在多年後對我們出演這套作品的首次舞台劇依然能夠感到驕傲，我希望能夠成為賦予了生命的千尋活下去」。<br />\n<br />\n製片人鈴本先生表示「John是一個不錯的人。我和宮崎也很喜歡他。希望他能在今次的舞台劇令千尋有所成長。」。<br />\n<br />\n在2018年因為參演舞台劇「Knights Tale」(ナイツ・テイル)而與上白石合作過的Caird對於能夠再會感到期待，更表示「終於得到機會再次和和魅力十足以及一起愈快地工作過的上白石再次合作了。」。<br />\n<br />\n上白石則愈快地表示「對放能夠成為這套超越了時間與國界，一直受到眾人喜愛的作品的其中一環感到十分榮幸」。"},{"pid":"89b12ee2ab5d9ef2678c58e607d9f92bbaa6d413","tid":2423676,"uid":55502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"導演仲要係Steve Jobs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2ca11d829122b760283af99774ced30cf03270","tid":2423676,"uid":45232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"舞台劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改編神作好大壓力<br />\n一唔好真係俾人屌到肺都穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce24783b63f7361d65b9f1205b3c3f72f9b6db63","tid":2423676,"uid":161467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb945942e02eddb3134988f0d1a03a6d0268edf","tid":2423676,"uid":213862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}